  "description": "An externally attractive, roomy and at the same time quite functional refrigerator from the BeSpoke designer series from the popular Samsung brand. The doors are equipped with a decorative front panel, which can be replaced with an analog in a different color if necessary. The device has two working chambers - cooling and freezing. Each of the compartments has both a separate door and its own circulation circuit, while the compressor itself has an inverter device and is provided with a 20-year brand warranty! Also note that the Samsung BeSpoke RB38C7B6AAP refrigerator uses an improved freezer - the freezing zone is equipped with the Cool Select + system, which allows the freezer to operate in light freezing or simple cooling mode. In this case, the freezer compartment turns into an auxiliary refrigeration chamber. The back wall is equipped with a Metal Cooling pad - this is a special metal surface that accumulates cold, which helps stabilize the internal microclimate. The refrigerator body is designed for installation close to walls and furniture. The outer rear wall has a safe external partition that isolates the condenser circuit.",
